-- Fidelity to provide retirement services to American Airlines
-- 
-- Mon Oct 27, 2014 12:33PM EDT
-- None



Oct 27 (Reuters) - Fidelity Investments said it would provide 401(k) retirement services to employees of American Airlines Group Inc <AAL.O>, beginning mid-2015.

The five-year agreement will service about 120,000 employees, Fidelity said. (http://bit.ly/12SoroM)